    "description": "In a world where everything can be counted and connected, will you rise to the occasion?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/d2d48c6335e4a5dc722821ae0a27e213.avif?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Build +30 different buildings<br></li><li> Manage your own custom train network.<br></li><li> Build new regions from the ground up.<br></li><li> Craft with your industrial buildings the materials you will need to strive for progress<br></li><li> Connect the different regions between them for collaboration.<br></li><li> Analyze the data of your city nodes and industry nodes in order to choose the right way forward</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/ab1febf045b18f75ceb78b0735b353e0.avif?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=616 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/e6815059e6ac1d24d785456fd27b665c.avif?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/7b59efcf74229851f226cfacd7a1bd5e.avif?t=1751644767\" width=308 height=272 /></span><br>Andy and company will help you while you manage everything. Sometimes they will offer you advice or be responsible for one action you command or they will just try to cheer you up.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/70662e1159aff46033faee6460f40f7e.avif?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=65 /></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/7e9c01ee799f4ce41ace3bd10ea48f8f.webp?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Create a nice park, build your  favorite restaurant and enjoy<br> the sounds of the city. In this mode you’ll be in control of the microdecisions of the game. Those decisions can be aesthetic (Whether the entertainment is a park or a shop) or can decide how an industrial building operates.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/d2aa886edfa51d4b4573667b9e1f21b3.webp?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Manage the different industrial zones to control the various productions of materials in order to be as efficient as possible. Also manage the movement of the workers, the most important resource of all.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/6a7c0e97f973f0c6f4f68ed05090fce3.webp?t=1751644767\" width=616 height=52 /></span><br>Connect all the regions you have created, allowing them to share the resources and grow together.<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/1addb24b2d789b10a4e0a04a4bb7f121.poster.avif?t=1751644767\" width=680 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/1addb24b2d789b10a4e0a04a4bb7f121.webm?t=1751644767\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052790/extras/1addb24b2d789b10a4e0a04a4bb7f121.mp4?t=1751644767\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
